data.description: Discover unparalleled luxury in this meticulously designed five bedrooms and three bathrooms within 3000 sq ft, seamlessly blending modern elegance with convenience. An inviting foyer leads to a formal dining space and a home office/ flex room, while the family room connects effortlessly to a gourmet kitchen boasting granite countertops, abundant amount of counter cabinets and counter space, premium SS appliances, a large island great for entertaining.  All the bedrooms are large with walk-in closets. The outdoor oasis, now featuring a private pool, expansive patio, and a screened-in porch, transforms the covered back patio into a tranquil retreat. The Master Suite offers seclusion with a spacious bath and custom designed walk-in closet.
